<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application>Gnopernicus</application></title>

<para>Installez <application>Gnopernicus</application> en lançant les commandes
suivantes&nbsp;:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=`pkg-config --variable=prefix ORBit-2.0` \
    --sysconfdir=/etc/gnome --localstatedir=/var/lib &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>
